{
  "stem": "21812.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I had heard about the Austrian Battalion.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was anxious to get into the Army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wanted to be there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- I don't know whether you remember it, but there was a newspaper called a very liberal newspaper.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they had written about the Austrian Battalion.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the reason they had written about it is because Archduke Otto and Archduke-- what was the other one?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I forgot the other, his brother-- were in that battalion.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So somehow I had an inkling that I-- and I wanted to be-- I was gung-ho.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was now a 100% American.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I wanted to forget everything that I ever knew about Vienna and Austria.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so I got to Camp Upton it was, the staging area.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my cousin went with me to Penn Station and put me on the train.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I guess my mother, once having to send me was enough, and he-- he-- we became very close.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We lived together, and we're still very close.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we get to Camp Upton and everybody else being shipped out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and by that time, I knew that I would be going to the Austrian Battalion, because I didn't than go with the other guys.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So sure enough, we were shipped to Camp Atterbury in-- outside of Indianapolis.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was the Austrian-- there was an Austrian Battalion.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that Austrian Battalion was the weirdest thing you can imagine because they had taken everybody from the Austrian-Hungarian Empire, not from Austria, but the old Austrian-Hungarian Empire, and put them into that-- that were not a citizen, and put them into that battalion.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was Archduke Otto and his brother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the-- kept on writing about this.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
